  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Studios </strong>are around 25m², and sleeps one to two people in twin beds. Studios do not have the possibility for extra beds.</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom suites </strong>are around 40m² and sleep two to four people. These suites have one twin bedroom and an additional sofa-bed in living room which sleeps one adult or two small children (Max 3 adults)</p>
<p><strong>Two bedroom suites</strong> are around 69m²-79m² and can sleep two to six people. Each suite has two twin bedrooms, plus a sofa-bed in living room which sleeps one adult or two small children (Max 5 adults). These suites are duplex.</p>
<p><strong>Three bedroom suites </strong>are around 68m²-98m² and sleep four to eight people. Each suite has three twin bedrooms,  plus a sofa-bed in living room which sleeps one adult or two small children (Max 7 adults). These suites are duplex.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>Please note that c<span>leaning is provided on request.</span><span></span></p>
<p><strong>Room and Suite Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Living room with additional sofa bed (no sofa in studios)</li>
<li>Kitchenette <span>with 2-ring hob, microwave or oven, coffee/tea maker, fridge and dishwasher</span></li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Sauna</li>
<li>Balcony</li>
<li>Drying closet</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathroom with shower</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li><span>Linen and towels </span></li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
